Insider Activity


Individual




Nachum Shamir



Mr. Nachum Shamir is President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Luminex Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Advanced Inhalation Therapies (AIT) Ltd., Luminex Corp., and invendo medical GmbH.
Mr. Shamir was previously employed as President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Given Imaging Ltd. and President & Chief Executive Officer by Kodak Versamark, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from The Hebrew University of Jerusalem and a graduate degree from Harvard University.



